And they quietly sing, heigh-ho,
heigh-- these are these guys.

00:31:20.915 --> 00:31:23.040
They know the right way
and wrong way to do things.

00:31:23.040 --> 00:31:23.850
And they'll point it out to you.

00:31:23.850 --> 00:31:25.350
They love to tell you,
you know, Jeff, that's

00:31:25.350 --> 00:31:26.391
the wrong way to do that.

00:31:26.391 --> 00:31:28.290
I'm on all these
famous journals.

00:31:28.290 --> 00:31:30.077
And all these other
guys in the journal

00:31:30.077 --> 00:31:32.160
