00:32:05.670 --> 00:32:06.890
is McDonald's.

00:32:06.890 --> 00:32:09.440
Some illiterate kid presses
the cheeseburger button.

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:12.260
And simultaneously, somebody
shoots a cow in Argentina.

00:32:12.260 --> 00:32:12.800
Bang!

00:32:12.800 --> 00:32:14.060
And everything in
between happens.

00:32:14.060 --> 00:32:15.050
And Smithers, come here.

00:32:15.050 --> 00:32:16.216
These are these guys, right?

00:32:16.216 --> 00:32:18.020
They want everything to work.

00:32:18.020 --> 00:32:22.970
And, ironically, in
Google, as in Amazon,

00:32:22.970 --> 00:32:26.310
