00:32:26.310 --> 00:32:27.350
It's not in the green.

00:32:27.350 --> 00:32:28.760
It's here, right?

00:32:28.760 --> 00:32:33.020
You're running a back-office,
very intricate supply

00:32:33.020 --> 00:32:36.870
chain is what you're doing, with
algorithms all over the place.

00:32:36.870 --> 00:32:39.230
So it's all about
efficiency and quality.

00:32:39.230 --> 00:32:41.650
Where the other one was
about innovation and growth,

00:32:41.650 --> 00:32:43.220
radical innovation
and growth, this

00:32:43.220 --> 00:32:44.840
is innovation to
make things more

00:32:44.840 --> 00:32:46.020
efficient to make them work.

00:32:46.020 --> 00:32:46.870
And the people who
run this-- we're

00:32:46.870 --> 00:32:48.410
going to call them engineers.

00:32:48.410 --> 00:32:50.527
It's all about security
and productivity,

00:32:50.527 --> 00:32:52.860
the whole idea of doing the
right way and the wrong way.

00:32:52.860 --> 00:32:55.502
So you see that these are quite
different from each other.

00:32:55.502 --> 00:32:56.960
So these people
are very good where

00:32:56.960 --> 00:32:58.280
there's large-scale projects.

00:32:58.280 --> 00:33:00.030
We're going to build
something really big,

00:33:00.030 --> 00:33:01.880
like this whole campus
up here at Google.

00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:03.860
And we're going to have a
right way and a wrong way.

00:33:03.860 --> 00:33:04.910
We're going to get
these people who

00:33:04.910 --> 00:33:07.100
have technical degrees--
engineering, medicine,

00:33:07.100 --> 00:33:08.109
the sciences.

00:33:08.109 --> 00:33:10.400
And what these people want
is they want responsibility.

00:33:10.400 --> 00:33:13.540
Because what they seek
is they seek process.

00:33:13.540 --> 00:33:17.630
And the reason they use process
is because what they have to do

00:33:17.630 --> 00:33:20.390
is take the vision
that the artist has,

00:33:20.390 --> 00:33:22.250
and they have to materialize it.

00:33:22.250 --> 00:33:24.876
They have to build the
stupid thing, right?

00:33:24.876 --> 00:33:26.750
And incidentally,
artists-- one of the things

