Lennon and McCartney-- you're
going to see this over and over

00:35:06.980 --> 00:35:07.710
again.

00:35:07.710 --> 00:35:09.770
You have to find the person
that makes you crazy.

00:35:09.770 --> 00:35:11.790
So I like superheroes.

